Chinese: 我认为有吸引力的文章

English: I do it probably 15-20 times a day,
be it job openings within CGI
or recent news releases from CGI
or articles that I feel are of interest.
Chinese: 我大概每天做这件事15到20次，
无论是CGI内部的职位空缺
还是CGI最近发布的新闻稿
或是我认为有意义的文章。
